GRID SYSTEM PART 2

12 1 Columns



Change the s1 to m1:

 <div class="col m1">
     <div class="box">
         1
   </div>
</div>

-- THEY WILL BE 12 COLUMNS BUT WHEN GET TO MEDIUM OR LESS THEY STACK TO ONE

and add also the class of s12

 <div class="col m1 s12">
     <div class="box">
        1
   </div>
</div>


This will stack all the columns when they get to small size

You give the m4 so it will be 4 3 columns big sizes medium but at small scream it will stack adding the s12 class:

 3 4 COLUMNS

 <div class="row">
        <div class="col m4 s12">
          <div class="box">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col m4 s12">
          <div class="box">2</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col m4 s12">
          <div class="box">3</div>
        </div>
      </div>

ALL CLASSES



