PULL AND PUSH

This is normal


  <div class="row">
        <div class="col s7">
          <div class="box">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s5">
          <div class="box">2</div>
        </div>
      </div>

This is applying push and pull

  <div class="row">
        <div class="col s7 push-s5">
          <div class="box">1</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col s5 pull-s7">
          <div class="box">2</div>
        </div>
      </div>

They look reverse.




